ARCHITECTURE NOTES FOR REFACTOR!!:
I was looking at this as a object oriented project. But since it's a game, it's more of a state machine.
OOP is more about models with internal mutable state.
State Machines (functional programming) is more about pure functions transformming game state.
State machines are much better for multiplayer games, especially ones like poker.



